recover_aio.Rd

For use on 'ncurlAio' when encountering a character conversion error 'embedded nul in string' (received data is not text data). This function allows recovery by retrieving the value as a raw vector.

recover_aio(aio)

Arguments

aio

an ncurlAio (object of class 'ncurlAio').

Value

The passed object (invisibly).

Details

A raw vector will be available at $data, as if convert = FALSE had been specified.

Note: calling this function on an unresolved Aio is an error and any resulting operation is not guaranteed.
